parameters:
It was much smoother than I had imagined. Fortunately, it seems
that I had a talent for 'magic', and I feel like I was a step
ahead of my classmates.

I was happy. Everyone called me a 'genius'. Even my father
praised me a lot...
I never doubted that I was the 'best'.

One day, suddenly... news of an incoming student with a special
treatment scholarship arrives.

『Special Treatment』... Such treatment is extremely rare in the
history of the academy, with only a few examples. It is usually
the nobles who want to enhance their reputation who approach the
academy, and at most, they are given preferential treatment.

However, this time it seems that it's not such a fake. The
academy was in turmoil due to an emergency situation.

But it has nothing to do with me. No matter what kind of 'genius'
they may be, I just have to overpower them with my own abilities.
